  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl03_LabelType\">Deep, compulsive greed gnaws at you.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Effects</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl03_LabelType\">Whenever monetary treasure is divided, you must end up with a greater share of that treasure than your companions or you&rsquo;re wracked with feelings of jealousy and ill will. When treasure is divided, if you do not end up with at least 10% more treasure than any other individual companion does, you have a hard time being helpful to your allies. You become irritable, and can&rsquo;t take the aid another action for the next week.</span></p>",
